sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Frontend as React Frontend
    participant Backend as Node.js Backend
    participant S3 as Amazon S3
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (PostGIS)

    User->>Frontend: Enter property details & select media files
    User->>Frontend: Click "Create Property"
    
    Note over Frontend,Backend: 1. Initialize Property & Request Upload URLs
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/properties (Property Data & Media Metadata)
    
    Backend->>DB: INSERT INTO properties
    DB-->>Backend: Return Property ID

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Backend,S3: 2. Generate Presigned URLs Phase
        Backend->>DB: INSERT INTO property_media (Status: Pending)
        Backend->>S3: Generate Presigned URLs (via AWS SDK)
        S3-->>Backend: Return Presigned URLs
    end
    
    Backend-->>Frontend: 201 Created (Return Property ID & Presigned URLs)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Frontend,S3: 3. Direct Media Upload Phase
        Frontend->>S3: PUT media files (using Presigned URLs)
        S3-->>Frontend: 200 OK (Upload Successful)
        
        Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/properties/{id}/media/{media_id} (confrim)
        Backend->>DB: UPDATE property_media (Status: Uploaded)
        DB-->>Backend: Acknowledge Update
    end
    Backend-->>Frontend: 200 OK (Confirmation Success)
    
    Frontend-->>User: Display success message & redirect to property page